Use the standard library
This is how to x_or_y of n and x and y:
   When n is less than 2, then:
      The answer is x
   End when
   Remember that i is 2
   Do this n times:
      When i is at most n, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      When remainder of n and i is 0, then:
         The answer is y
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is x
Now you know